WorldStage Newsonline– The Initiates Plc. (TIP), a Port Harcourt Nigeria based professional waste management company has confirmed that Dvcf Oil & Gas Plc, a substantial shareholder in the company  had sold 997,012 units of its holdings in the company at N0.70 per share  which amounted to N697,908.4. A notice to the Nigerian Stock Exchange signed today by Olaide Odejobi, Company Secretary, said the transaction took place on August 10, 11 and 12, 2020. Similarly, Dvcf Oil & Gas Plc  had on July 27th, 2020 sold 649 units of its Holdings in the company at N0.70 per share. TIP delivers Waste Management, Industrial Cleaning and Decontamination services to both Private and Public sectors.